  <brief_title>Retinal Nerve Fiber Layer Thickness Measurement on Parapapillary Atrophy With the Cirrus High-Definition (HD) Optical Coherence Tomography (OCT)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Retinal Nerve Fiber Layer Thickness Measurement on Parapapillary Atrophy With</official_title>
